WEBVTT

00:10:27.650 --> 00:10:30.356
ktorú objavil môj kolega Tom Eisner,

00:10:30.356 --> 00:10:32.299
viedla tieto svetlušky

00:10:32.299 --> 00:10:35.697
k tomu, aby vzali
svoje jasné svetlá von do noci

00:10:35.697 --> 00:10:39.380
s úmyslom zrady.

00:10:39.380 --> 00:10:41.010
Môj kolega Jim Lloyd

00:10:41.010 --> 00:10:43.495
ich nazval „femme fatales“.

00:10:43.495 --> 00:10:46.413
Tieto samičky prišli na to,
ako sa zamerať na

00:10:46.413 --> 00:10:50.224
samčekov iných druhov.

00:10:50.224 --> 00:10:52.124
Takže lov začína predátorom –

00:10:52.124 --> 00:10:54.171
je tu zobrazená dole vľavo,

00:10:54.171 --> 00:10:56.218
kde ticho sedí

00:10:56.218 --> 00:10:59.350
a načúva konverzácii dvorenia

00:10:59.350 --> 00:11:00.790
svojej budúcej koristi.